title: Bilko - 50th anniversary DVD
description:
This is an ISO image of disc 1 and includes the special features. 

Programs from 1955 are:-

NEW RECRUITS
THE WAC
THE HORSE
THE EATING CONTEST
BIVOUAC

Special features are:-

Nick @ Nite promo taping for Sgt. Bilko movie with Dan Aykroyd and Phil Hartman.
Phil Hartman episode intros for Nick @ Nite
The Ed Sullivan Show clip
Allan Melvin (Cpl. Henshaw) episode introductions.
Lost audition show.
1956 Emmy awards highlights.
Phil Silvers on The Dick Cavett Show.
Friars Stag Roast for Humphrey Bogart (audio)
